How to play

Send a boost to your favourite podcast on Fountain and let them know how much their podcast means to you. The top two boosts (by value) every week will win a Bitrefill Balance Card with $50 of credit. Winners will be announced every Friday on Fountain's Twitter.

Download the Fountain app

Fountain is the podcast app that pays and is available on iOS or Android

Connect your ZEBEDEE account to increase your limits

To send a boost larger than 600,000 sats you will need to connect your ZEBEDEE account. You will find the option to connect to ZEBEDEE in your Wallet or Profile menu in the Fountain app. Simply the follow the steps to create a new account or to connect to an existing one.
